preference.name: QS_BBOX_GENERATION_FROM_NX_ENABLED
preference.preference_description: Enables or disables the generation of bounding box data from the UGPART-BBOX form of an NX dataset. Valid Values: true - Enables the generation of bounding box data needed by the cacheless spatial search mechanism. false - Disables the generation of bounding box data needed by the cacheless spatial search mechanism.
